Bug.WithOutStack:
This issue was previously reported as Bug#96766 on 3.1M7. A fix was applied and
released in 3.1RC1. However the fix is only partial and there is still a problem.

The cause of this issue is the logic in the getLinkText() method of
JavaStackTraceHyperlink.java. This method is intended to return a substring from
a line which contains a link. The substring should be the link text. 

